 argue that all three tensor structures of $\\langle TTT\\rangle$ in the\nfree-field basis are nonzero in interacting CFTs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Dec 2017 16:53:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Dec 2017 15:44:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-15"}
