s of \"cold feedback mode\" and \"hot feedback\nmode\" to replace the currently used ones.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Dec 2017 19:12:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Mar 2018 10:26:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-02"}
