locities. However, importantly, the alternating\noptimization provides some gain in computational time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Dec 2017 19:51:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Mar 2018 17:32:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-09"}
