athrm{crit}}\\gtrsim40$ Mm) and eruptive flares\n($h_{\\mathrm{crit}}\\lesssim40$ Mm). It discriminates better than\n$\\Delta\\varphi$, implying that the decay of the confining field plays a\nstronger role than its orientation at different heights.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Dec 2017 07:08:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-14"}
