ay to revise the standards\nfor network analysis, from the pairwise interactions between nodes to the\nglobal properties of networks including community detection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Dec 2017 11:00:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Mar 2018 13:23:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-09"}
